        <h2>Our Origin Story</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Sprint-Tribe, your number one destination to top quality sprinting gear and everything related to
          sprinting. Sprint-Tribe was founded in 1994 by Thapelo Mokgantshane in the village of Ramotswa after noticing 
          the struggle of locally talented young boys to afford gear to compete and take their game to the next level.
          Founded in a small storeroom by an ambitious mind, Sprint-Tribe managed to sky rocket in success, achieving 
          many accolades such as winning Best African sports brand in the year 2007 at the African Excellence awards which
          were hosted at Rabat in Morocco.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Sprint-Tribe has a mission to bridge the gap between talent and opportunity by delivering affordable, high
        perfomance sprint gear
        </p>

